About us
.
Himalaya Television, named after the mighty Himalayas, is a channel that has a vision beyond the conventional vogues of broadcasting. Our ambition is not solely to show but also to raise awareness of human issues and embrace the heterogeneous needs of a multicultural society. Himalaya Television reaches out to all the people of Nepal from the plains of the Terai to the high lands of the Himalayas and to those struggling for their livelihood abroad. Himalaya Television Network (HTV), one of the top premium infotainment Satellite Television channels in the Nation started in the year 2010 and has been successfully able to create its identity in a short span of time. 
.

About Harke Haldar :

Harke Haldar is a funny weekly Nepali comedy (drama) serial on Kantipur Television HD from one of the rural village of Nepal, where the story revolves around the main character ex. Hawaldar (Harke ) along with his troublesome neighbors. Harke Haldar is the most viewed television programs in Nepal showed in Kantipur Television HD. This is also a social serial that resembles typical Nepali Society.

snippet.title: The Kapil Sharma Show Season 2 | Kajol Meets "Ajay Devgn" | Ep 284 | FE | 3 Dec 2022
snippet.description:
Synopsis: Kajol Meets "Ajay Devgn" 
 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
The host, Kapil Sharma, makes a rocking entry to the stage and talks about how parents are with their children. He compliments Archana Puran Singh and they share a hilarious banter. He shares some funny talks and how now times are different from the past and how children are also smart now. Then the evergreen, Kajol makes an entry, and Kapil introduces her, and she talks about her film Salaam Venky and what it depicts. This starts a hilarious night of fun, watch the full episode to know more.

Show Name: The Kapil Sharma Show Season 2 
Guests - Kajol, Vishal Jethwa, and Revathi.
Episode: 284 - 3 Dec 2022
Producers: Kapil Sharma, Salman Khan, Deepak Dhar
